Bring a large pot of water to a boil. In a large skillet saute leek in olive oil until slightly browned. Add asparagus and saute until cooked through. Add roasted pepper *and season with salt and pepper. Cook pasta 1 minute less than the package directions. Drain pasta reserving 1 cup of the cooking water. Add cooking water to sauce and bring to a simmer. Add pasta to sauce and toss. Remove from heat. Add cheese and basil; toss to combine and serve.